overview_of_class:
Introduction to landmark insights into quantitative biology. Random genetic processes, gene expression, cell adaption, cell cycle,developmental morphogens, phylgenomics.

Prerequisites: 215; 217 or 219; MATH 22 or 224; PHYSICS 130-1,2,3 OR 135-1,2,3.
name: Quantitative Analysis of Biology
title: WCAS BIOL_SCI 354-0-1 Quantitative Analysis of Biology
enrl_requirement: Enrollment Requirements: Students must have taken BIOL_SCI 215-0, (BIOL_SCI 217-0 or 219-0), (MATH 220-0 or 224-0), and (PHYSICS 130-1,2,3 or 135-1,2,3) in order to register for this course.
